'''中國分裂論'''是一種[[意識形態|意識形態]]論點，由多位政治人物、学者以及社运人士提出。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/simp/hi/newsid_7950000/newsid_7951100/7951106.stm |title=藏独思潮：从藏青会说起 |access-date=2021-12-11 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308093603/http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/simp/hi/newsid_7950000/newsid_7951100/7951106.stm }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/hx-12042018102419.html |title=专访藏独领袖：“中间道路”和藏独不冲突 |access-date=2021-12-11 |archive-date=2022-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220518123240/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/hx-12042018102419.html }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/focus_on_china/2013/07/130701_cr_split |title=點評中國:分裂中港台，分裂中國論 |access-date=2015-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151225231056/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/focus_on_china/2013/07/130701_cr_split |archive-date=2015-12-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>是認為[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]（以下简称[[中國|中國]]）未來將分裂成多個國家的看法。

